B\u00c1O GI\u00c1 THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T CHUNG C\u01af, NH\u00c0 PH\u1ed0, BI\u1ec6T TH\u1ef0 TR\u1eccN G\u00d3I 2024<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n<p>Byzan Design xin g\u1eedi <strong>b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong> tr\u1ecdn g\u00f3i c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng trong n\u0103m 2024. Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch l\u01b0u \u00fd b\u1ea3ng gi\u00e1 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho c\u00e1c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n, showroom\u2026<\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\">\r\n\r\n<\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13822\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bao-gia-dich-vu-2024.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"768\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bao-gia-dich-vu-2024.png 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bao-gia-dich-vu-2024-300x225.png 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/bao-gia-dich-vu-2024-768x576.png 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p>V\u1edbi quy tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c minh b\u1ea1ch, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cam k\u1ebft mang t\u1edbi cho qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea3n thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9c \u0111\u00e1o chu\u1ea9n hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. <strong>Byzan Design<\/strong> theo \u0111u\u1ed5i chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u chuy\u00ean s\u00e2u phong c\u00e1ch hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i; kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t \u0111a phong c\u00e1ch, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c tr\u00ean th\u1ebf m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.\u00a0<\/p>\r\n<p>T\u1ea1i Byzan, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi <strong>b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong> mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed, b\u1edfi th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec l\u00e0 mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed. V\u1edbi kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n 10 n\u0103m trong ngh\u1ec1, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00fac k\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c r\u1eb1ng: \u201cB\u1ecf 1 \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u00ed thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf, gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 100 \u0111\u1ed3ng chi ph\u00ed thi c\u00f4ng &#8211; Mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed 1 \u0111\u1ed3ng ph\u00ed thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf s\u1ebd m\u1ea5t 100 \u0111\u1ed3ng chi ph\u00ed thi c\u00f4ng.\u201d Do \u0111\u00f3, gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 hay chung c\u01b0, nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1,&#8230; tuy kh\u00f4ng l\u1edbn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ee3i d\u00e2y li\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a Byzan v\u1edbi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng v\u1edbi ch\u00ednh ng\u00f4i nh\u00e0 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\r\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><\/figure>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:image --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:heading --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<h2><strong>B\u00c1O GI\u00c1 THI\u1ebeT K\u1ebe THI C\u00d4NG N\u1ed8I TH\u1ea4T CHUNG C\u01af, BI\u1ec6T TH\u1ef0, NH\u00c0 PH\u1ed0, LI\u1ec0N K\u1ec0 M\u1edaI NH\u1ea4T 2024<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:group --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\">\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:media-text {\"mediaPosition\":\"right\",\"mediaId\":8014,\"mediaType\":\"image\",\"mediaWidth\":35,\"verticalAlignment\":\"center\"} --><\/span>\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text alignwide has-media-on-the-right is-stacked-on-mobile is-vertically-aligned-center\" style=\"grid-template-columns: auto 35%;\">\r\n<figure class=\"wp-block-media-text__media\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"360\" height=\"360\" class=\"wp-image-8014 size-full aligncenter\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/nhan-bao-gia-1.gif\" alt=\"\" \/><\/span><\/figure>\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\"><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span>B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chung c\u01b0, bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1, nh\u00e0 ph\u1ed1&#8230; chi ph\u00ed thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c n\u00e0y lu\u00f4n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, di\u1ec7n t\u00edch m\u1ed7i c\u0103n h\u1ed9 l\u00e0 kh\u00e1c nhau, nhu c\u1ea7u s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng v\u00e0 s\u1edf th\u00edch c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n c\u0169ng kh\u00e1c nhau, do \u0111\u00f3 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch kh\u00f4ng gian, lo\u1ea1i v\u1eadt li\u1ec7u v\u00e0 kh\u1ed1i l\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00e0 3 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 ch\u00ednh quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1edbi t\u1ed5ng m\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ea7u t\u01b0 c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.<\/div>\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">Nh\u00ecn chung, thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t chia th\u00e0nh 2 ph\u1ea7n ch\u00ednh:<\/div>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">Thi c\u00f4ng n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u1ea7n th\u00f4: bao g\u1ed3m qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh th\u00e1o d\u1ee1, \u0111i h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng \u0111i\u1ec7n n\u01b0\u1edbc, thi c\u00f4ng tr\u1ea7n, t\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 s\u00e0n.<\/li>\r\n<li class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">Thi c\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t: Ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch, ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, ph\u00f2ng \u0103n, ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, ph\u00f2ng t\u1eafm, logia.<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">Hi\u1ec7n nay c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f4ng ty b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 c\u00e1c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n c\u0103n h\u1ed9 giao th\u00f4 t\u00ednh theo m\u00e9t vu\u00f4ng s\u00e0n v\u00e0 chia th\u00e0nh d\u1ea1ng c\u00e1c g\u00f3i. Tuy nhi\u00ean, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, v\u1eadt t\u01b0 nh\u00e0 th\u1ea7u cung c\u1ea5p c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 d\u1ef1 tr\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ebft chi ph\u00ed c\u00e1c h\u1ea1ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n thi\u1ec7n m\u1ed9t c\u0103n h\u1ed9. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn t\u00ecnh tr\u1ea1ng v\u1eadt t\u01b0 v\u00e0 thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb k\u00e9m ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng, ph\u00e1t sinh ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed sau khi \u0111\u00e3 thi c\u00f4ng. Byzan g\u1ee3i \u00fd c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t thi c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 sau:<\/div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Chi Ph\u00ed Thi C\u00f4ng = Kh\u1ed1i L\u01b0\u1ee3ng Thi C\u00f4ng Th\u1ef1c T\u1ebf x \u0110\u01a1n Gi\u00e1 C\u1ed1 \u0110\u1ecbnh (*)<\/strong><br \/><strong>(*) t\u00ednh theo \u0111\u01a1n gi\u00e1 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00e1o gi\u00e1<\/strong><\/div>\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">M\u1ed7i d\u1ef1 \u00e1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 k\u1ebft c\u1ea5u, ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac, phong c\u00e1ch v\u00e0 di\u1ec7n t\u00edch kh\u00e1c nhau. Y\u00eau c\u1ea7u, mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a gia ch\u1ee7 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 gi\u1ed1ng nhau. Do v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu c\u00f3 nhu c\u1ea7u, kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng n\u00ean trao \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 g\u1eedi \u0111\u1ea7y \u0111\u1ee7 th\u00f4ng tin v\u1ec1 c\u0103n h\u1ed9, mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh v\u1ec1 cho Byzan \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u01b0 v\u1ea5n v\u00e0 nh\u1eadn <strong>b\u00e1o gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf thi c\u00f4ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac &#8211; n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t<\/strong> chi ti\u1ebft nh\u1ea5t!<\/div>\r\n<div class=\"wp-block-media-text__content\">\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph {\"align\":\"left\",\"placeholder\":\"N\u1ed9i dung...\",\"fontSize\":\"normal\"} --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<h2 class=\"has-text-align-left has-normal-font-size\"><strong>QUY TR\u00ccNH L\u00c0M VI\u1ec6C CHUY\u00caN NGHI\u1ec6P T\u1ea0I BYZAN DESIGN<\/strong><\/h2>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<\/div>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:heading --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u mang \u0111\u1ebfn cho b\u1ea1n s\u1ef1 an t\u00e2m, tin t\u01b0\u1edfng tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi cam k\u1ebft th\u01b0\u1edfng ph\u1ea1t v\u00e0 n\u0103ng l\u1ef1c l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng th\u00ec Byzan x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n tham kh\u1ea3o, tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 t\u00ecm hi\u1ec3u chu\u1ea9n m\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0nh N\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t Hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i. Tr\u00e2n tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c mang \u0111\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb ch\u00e2n th\u1ef1c nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ebfn m\u1ed7i kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho \u0111\u1ebfn gi\u00e1 th\u00e0nh s\u1ea3n ph\u1ea9m \u0111\u1ec3 qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi Byzan s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1ea3i nghi\u1ec7m th\u00fa v\u1ecb, vui th\u00edch v\u00e0 an t\u00e2m.<\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-13838 size-full\" title=\"byzan-dam-bao-chat-luong-thi-cong\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/301de797278486dadf9514.jpg\" alt=\"bao-gia-thiet-ke-noi-that\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1059\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/301de797278486dadf9514.jpg 1800w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/301de797278486dadf9514-300x177.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/301de797278486dadf9514-1024x602.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/301de797278486dadf9514-768x452.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/301de797278486dadf9514-1536x904.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><strong>B\u01b0\u1edbc 1: Ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng<\/strong><\/p>\r\n<p>B\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a quy tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn y\u00eau c\u1ea7u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng tin c\u1ee7a qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft quy m\u00f4 v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a c\u00f4ng tr\u00ecnh c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng. Sau khi ti\u1ebfp nh\u1eadn th\u00f4ng tin d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1eeb kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng, Byzan se\u0303 \u0111\u1ea1\u0306t li\u0323ch he\u0323n KTS tu\u031b v\u00e2\u0301n tre\u0302n ba\u0309n ve\u0303 m\u1ea1\u0306t b\u0103\u0300ng co\u0301 s\u0103\u0303n h