dbi H\u0110TK nh\u00e0 th\u1ed5 c\u01b0:<\/p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m 70% ph\u00ed thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 1,1 t\u1ef7 tr\u1edf l\u00ean.<\/li>\r\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m 50% ph\u00ed thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 700 tri\u1ec7u \u2013 1,1 t\u1ef7 (VN\u0110).<\/li>\r\n<li>Gi\u1ea3m 30% ph\u00ed thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf v\u1edbi \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 t\u1eeb 500 \u2013 700 tri\u1ec7u (VN\u0110).<\/li>\r\n<\/ul>\r\n<p><em>Khi kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Ki\u1ebfn Tr\u00fac &amp; thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u00e1 thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf Ki\u1ebfn Tr\u00fac &amp; N\u1ed9i Th\u1ea5t c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0: 350.000\/m2\u00a0<\/em><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:list --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- \/wp:paragraph --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><!-- wp:list --><\/span><\/p>\r\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 100%;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-13840\" src=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b2a9b4247437d5698c2616-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1059\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b2a9b4247437d5698c2616-1.jpg 1800w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b2a9b4247437d5698c2616-1-300x177.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b2a9b4247437d5698c2616-1-1024x602.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b2a9b4247437d5698c2616-1-768x452.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/03\/b2a9b4247437d5698c2616-1-1536x904.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max